<h2 id="path-b-google-scholar-alerts-20-min">Path B: Google Scholar Alerts (20 min)</h2>

<h3 id="1-set-up-your-google-scholar-profile-5-min">1. Set up your Google Scholar profile (5 min)</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Go to <a href="https://scholar.google.com/">scholar.google.com</a></li>
  <li>Click ‚ÄúMy Profile‚Äù (you‚Äôll need a Google account)</li>
  <li>Fill in your name, affiliation, and areas of interest</li>
